      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine is strong and reliable, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. While the exterior shows some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all major systems, including the air conditioning and electronics, are fully functional. It is a dependable car that is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
