    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings consistent with regular use. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat, and while the air conditioning works, it takes a moment to get cold. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s an honest, functional car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
