    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional specimen, currently maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a motorcar that has been preserved to exacting standards. Its impeccable exterior finish is matched only by a pristine interior, reflecting a history of fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. This is an uncompromising offering for those who demand nothing less than automotive perfection.",
